  <entry>
    <title>How to build your blog?</title>
    <link href="/2023/11/18/How-to-build-your-blog/"/>
    <url>/2023/11/18/How-to-build-your-blog/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="环境依赖"><a href="#环境依赖" class="headerlink" title="环境依赖"></a>环境依赖</h2><ol><li>git</li><li>hexo </li><li>nodejs</li><li>ssh</li></ol><h3 id="环境搭建"><a href="#环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="环境搭建"></a>环境搭建</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">安装</span><br>sudo pacman -S git nodejs openssh<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">测试</span><br>git version <br>node -v <br>npm -v <br>ssh -V<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建本地博客"><a href="#创建本地博客" class="headerlink" title="创建本地博客"></a>创建本地博客</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo init blog_name<br>cd blog_name<br>npm install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="主题更换"><a href="#主题更换" class="headerlink" title="主题更换"></a>主题更换</h2><p>从github 下载想要的主题</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">cd themes<br>git clone https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid.git<br>mv hexo-theme-fluid fluid<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更改‘~&#x2F;blog_name&#x2F;_config.yml’文件中的themes的内容</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">theme: landscape <br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">--&gt;</span><span class="language-bash"></span><br><span class="language-bash">theme: fluid</span> <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="本地渲染"><a href="#本地渲染" class="headerlink" title="本地渲染"></a>本地渲染</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo g # 渲染博客<br>hexo s # 在本地 http://localhost:4000 打开博客<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建必要的页面"><a href="#创建必要的页面" class="headerlink" title="创建必要的页面"></a>创建必要的页面</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">创建关于页</span><br>hexo new page about <br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">创建分类页</span><br>hexo new page category<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">创建标签页</span><br>hexo new page tag<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更改~&#x2F;blog_name&#x2F;source&#x2F;about&#x2F;index.md文件内容</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">---<br>title: about<br>date: 2023-11-18 18:55:12<br>---<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">--&gt;</span><span class="language-bash"></span><br><span class="language-bash"></span><br>---<br>title: about<br>layout: about<br>date: 2023-11-18 18:55:12<br>---<br>这里写关于页的正文，支持 Markdown, HTML<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="gitub端部署"><a href="#gitub端部署" class="headerlink" title="gitub端部署"></a>gitub端部署</h2><h3 id="ssh连接github"><a href="#ssh连接github" class="headerlink" title="ssh连接github"></a>ssh连接github</h3><ol><li>生成ssh密钥<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;邮箱&quot; # 需要将邮箱给成你自己的邮箱，执行后一直回车即可<br>cd ~/.ssh<br>cat id_rsa.pub  # 查看生成的本地密钥<br>复制终端输出的内容<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>github设置<br>  github -&gt; settings -&gt; SSH and GPG keys -&gt; New SSH key<br>  将复制的内容粘贴至key目标框中，Title可以为任意内容。</li><li>验证<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">ssh -T git@github.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>当终端输出不报错，则表示使用ssh成功连接至github</li></ol><h3 id="github创建仓库"><a href="#github创建仓库" class="headerlink" title="github创建仓库"></a>github创建仓库</h3><p>github -&gt; your respositories -&gt; New<br>repositry name 必须为<font color=red>your_github_name.github.io</font></p><h2 id="将本地博客部署到github"><a href="#将本地博客部署到github" class="headerlink" title="将本地博客部署到github"></a>将本地博客部署到github</h2><ol><li>再次更改~&#x2F;bolg_name&#x2F;_config.yml文件<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">deploy:<br>  type: &#x27;&#x27;<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">--&gt;</span><span class="language-bash"></span><br><span class="language-bash"></span><br>deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repo: http://github.com/5huanghuai/5huanghuai.github.io.git<br>  branch: main<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>渲染本地博客并同步到github<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save # hexo 自动部署发布工具<br>hexo g # 本地渲染<br>hexo s # 本地查看<br>hexo d # 同步至github<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>部署成功后，网址<br><a href="http://5huanghuai.github.io/">http://5huanghuai.github.io</a></li></ol><h2 id="添加新文章"><a href="#添加新文章" class="headerlink" title="添加新文章"></a>添加新文章</h2><ol><li>hexo new ‘文章名称’</li><li>在～&#x2F;blog_name&#x2F;source&#x2F;_posts&#x2F;文章名称.md 修改文章内容</li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
